title: NBA Draftapalooza Part 4: Winners & Losers With Kevin O’Connor and Ryen Russillo
description:
The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Ryen Russillo and Kevin O’Connor to discuss winners and losers from the 2022 NBA draft.

Host: Bill Simmons
Guests: Kevin O’Connor and Ryen Russillo
Producer: Kyle Crichton
